abstract: Penn State wins its fifth NCAA wrestling championship in six years.

headline.print_headline: Penn State Wins Another N.C.A.A. Crown
headline.main: Penn State Wins Another N.C.A.A. Crown in Wrestling

snippet: Penn State clinched its fifth N.C.A.A. wrestling championship in six years with 114 points and the finals still to go.
lead_paragraph: Penn State clinched its fifth N.C.A.A. wrestling championship in six years with 114 points and the finals still to go.
